# Datasets Used in This Repository

This project uses the following datasets for XGBoost paper verification experiments:

- HIGGS
- Adult (UCI Census Income)
- Allstate Claims Severity
- MQ2008 (LETOR 4.0)
- Criteo 1TB Click Logs (day_2 to day_5 files)

## 1. Download the datasets

### HIGGS
- Dataset page: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/HIGGS
- Direct download: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/machine-learning-databases/00280/HIGGS.csv.gz

### Adult (UCI Census Income)
- Dataset page: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/adult
- adult.data: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/machine-learning-databases/adult/adult.data
- adult.test: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/machine-learning-databases/adult/adult.test

### Allstate Claims Severity
- Kaggle data page: https://www.kaggle.com/c/allstate-claims-severity/data

### MQ2008 (LETOR 4.0)
- Official page: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/letor-learning-rank-information-retrieval/letor-4-0/

### Criteo 1TB Click Logs
- Dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/criteo/CriteoClickLogs/tree/main/

## 2. Place files in this folder structure

Keep your dataset files under the data folder exactly like this:

```text
