|-- adult/
|   |-- adult.data
|   |-- adult.names
|   |-- adult.test
|   |-- Index
|   `-- old.adult.names
|-- allstate_raw/
|   `-- train_set.csv
`-- MQ2008/
    |-- min.txt
    |-- NULL.txt
    |-- Querylevelnorm.txt
    |-- readme.txt
    |-- S1.txt
    |-- S2.txt
    |-- S3.txt
    |-- S4.txt
    |-- S5.txt
    |-- Fold1/
    |   |-- test.txt
    |   |-- train.txt
    |   `-- vali.txt
    |-- Fold2/
    |   |-- test.txt
    |   |-- train.txt
    |   `-- vali.txt
    |-- Fold3/
    |   |-- test.txt
    |   |-- train.txt
    |   `-- vali.txt
    |-- Fold4/
    |   |-- test.txt
    |   |-- train.txt
    |   `-- vali.txt
    `-- Fold5/
        |-- test.txt
        |-- train.txt
        `-- vali.txt
```

## 3. Notes

- Verification scripts in verification/ use relative paths like ../data/...
- If you download archives (.gz, .zip, .7z, .rar), extract files so names and paths match the tree above.
